name: FormatProtection
description: Represents the format protection of a range object.

properties.name: locked
properties.description: Indicates if Excel locks the cells in the object. A null value indicates that the entire range doesn't have uniform lock setting.

properties.name: formulaHidden
properties.description: Indicates if Excel hides the formula for the cells in the range. A null value indicates that the entire range doesn't have uniform formula hidden setting.
